org.gradoop.temporal.model.impl.layout

Class TemporalGVELayout

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gradoop.temporal.model.impl.layout.TemporalGVELayout
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GraphCollectionLayout<TemporalGraphHead,TemporalVertex,TemporalEdge>, Layout<TemporalVertex,TemporalEdge>, LogicalGraphLayout<TemporalGraphHead,TemporalVertex,TemporalEdge>

    public class TemporalGVELayout
extends Object
implements LogicalGraphLayout<TemporalGraphHead,TemporalVertex,TemporalEdge>, GraphCollectionLayout<TemporalGraphHead,TemporalVertex,TemporalEdge>
    Represents a temporal graph or graph collection using three separate datasets:
    1. a dataset containing the temporal graph heads which are the metadata of logical graphs
    2. a dataset containing the temporal vertices
    3. a dataset containing the temporal edges
